Consider the following test case:
---
CREATE TABLE v0 ( v2 , v3 NOT NULL , v4 CHECK( 10 ) CHECK( v3 NOT LIKE 'SM PKG' ) NOT NULL UNIQUE NOT NULL , v5 NOT NULL , v1 ) ;
CREATE VIEW v6 ( v7 ) AS SELECT CAST ( ( SELECT coalesce ( sum ( DISTINCT v2 ) , v4 , v1 ) FROM v0 WHERE v1 = v1 GROUP BY v2 HAVING v2 > 'GERMANY' ) AS ) FROM v0 ;
SELECT AVG ( DISTINCT julianday ( ( SELECT coalesce ( max ( v7 ) OVER( ORDER BY v7 ) , max ( v7 ) OVER( ORDER BY v7 ) ) ) ) ) , count ( v7 ) FROM v6 WHERE v7 = 10 AND v7 >= '0' ;
---

In latest chrunk and release code, it triggers an assertion in debug build.
